sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant QueueProxy as Knative Activator /<br/>Queue-Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Engine<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8086/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Caikit: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
        Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012, mTLS (Istio)
        QueueProxy->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption (pod-internal)
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
        Caikit-->>QueueProxy: HTTP response
        QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,Caikit: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: gRPC call (NlpService)<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
        Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward request<br/>gRPC/HTTP2/8012, mTLS (Istio)
        QueueProxy->>Caikit: gRPC(h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption (pod-internal)
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
        Caikit-->>QueueProxy: gRPC response
        QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
        Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Client,Caikit: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation
        Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward (mTLS)
        QueueProxy->>Caikit: HTTP/8080 (mTLS)
        Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC stream/8033 (localhost)
        loop Streaming tokens
            TGIS-->>Caikit: Token chunk
            Caikit-->>QueueProxy: SSE chunk
            QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward chunk
            Gateway-->>Client: SSE token
        end
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
        Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086, PERMISSIVE mTLS
        Caikit-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over TGIS,S3: Flow 5: Model Loading (Startup)
        Note right of S3: KServe storage initializer<br/>downloads model at pod start
        S3-->>TGIS: Model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, AWS IAM
        Note right of TGIS: Model loaded into GPU memory<br/>from /mnt/models
    end
